{"tid":1754504,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[區選之後] 保持警覺謙卑心態","createTime":"2019-11-25T08:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T12:18:25.000Z","uid":2634,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ffc187b4c0fcf38384af109e8283d7d079101733","tid":1754504,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:40:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不要被短暫「勝利」沖昏頭腦</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">「謙卑、謙卑、再謙卑！」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聚焦五大訴求<br />\n強調真雙普選<br />\n毋忘被捕手足<br />\n謹記烈士遺志<br />\n<br />\n時刻警覺謙卑<br />\n不斷檢討改進<br />\n勿信陰謀詭計<br />\n資訊高質無誤<br />\n<br />\n手足互相鼓勵<br />\n切忌圍爐取暖<br />\n爭取最大民意<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 願榮光歸香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n不分化，不割席，不篤灰<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有日我哋必定喺煲底相認</span></span></strong></span></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpm7soCO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpm7soCO.jpg&h=00de3c25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9fd190014e95740c585f21e4ea2a33d675542c9","tid":1754504,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:41:43.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕不分化、絕不割席、絕不篤灰</span></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"78c223a643c34754b4e3e028177d8aa44396c7e0","tid":1754504,"uid":281756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:41:46.000Z","msg":"推"}